{"tid":588834,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[跪求]有冇人知呢足球動畫叫咩名？","createTime":"2018-03-11T13:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T13:31:31.000Z","uid":169807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"84efdfbae9b54c2fcbf08694344a81648d6d79c0","tid":588834,"uid":169807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T13:18:10.000Z","msg":"好耐之前係有線兒童台睇過<br />\n係講男主角成日要同班怪獸或者動物對戰，好似世界盃咁<br />\n因為自己呀爸當年輸左場波所以變成左做隻噴火龍<br />\n所以男主角同班隊友就一直比賽想幫佢呀爸變番做人<br />\n最後個場好似係個山洞既地方打<br />\n好似話如果佢輸左都會一樣變怪獸定變石像<br />\n其他野就唔記得啦<br />\n有冇Ching 知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a6fe793346cf430e2ff21b5373dd4ae02a9910b","tid":588834,"uid":8867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T13:22:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"100fc9f5782e3c6cfbbe3b4a26963026d49a4f28","tid":588834,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T13:23:24.000Z","msg":"閃電11人?"},{"pid":"4174cc840074481792894beecc0ae4c4cd8c873c","tid":588834,"uid":169807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"100fc9f5782e3c6cfbbe3b4a26963026d49a4f28","tid":588834,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T13:23:24.000Z","msg":"閃電11人?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T13:31:31.000Z","msg":"閃電11人太新啦<br />\n套野應該係80年代野<br />\n個陣兒童台播緊男兒當踢波(意甲小旋風 )"}]}